---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | SDub Media Nashville Video Production" description="SDub Media is a Nashville video production company built around recurring content. We help businesses show up on video every week, and shoot a few weddings a year.">
<section>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>One Team, One System,<br>Same Quality Every Week</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">SDub Media is a Nashville video production company built around one idea: businesses need to show up on video consistently, not just once. We build the production system so your content actually gets made, week after week, without the chaos.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background: var(--soft);">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">Why recurring</span>
    <h2>One Video Won't Move Your Business. Fifty Will.</h2>
    <p>Most companies treat video as an event. They save up, book a big shoot, post it once, and then go quiet for six months. It feels productive. It rarely works.</p>
    <p>Showing up on camera is a habit, not a moment. The brands that win attention are the ones in front of their audience every week with content that looks and sounds like them. The hard part was never the camera. It was the consistency: the planning, the scheduling, the editing, the follow-through.</p>
    <p>That is the part we own. We design a production rhythm around your calendar, batch the work so it is efficient, and keep the style consistent so every piece feels like one brand. You get a pipeline that does not stall the moment things get busy.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">The model in action</span>
    <h2>What That Actually Looks Like</h2>
    <p>Coldwell Banker Southern Realty is the clearest example. They have eight offices across Tennessee, and we work across them. We have shot at six locations so far, and the relationship runs in several formats at once.</p>
    <p>There is a weekly series filmed with the owner at the main office in Nashville. There are monthly headshot days, rotating through the offices one at a time so agents can come in for an updated headshot. We produce recurring content in their in-house podcast room, and we cover their major live events, where they bring in speakers to address all the offices. We also work with their luxury division.</p>
    <p>That is the whole point: not a one-off shoot, but a steady stream of content across formats, produced on a schedule. Same quality every time, without anyone on their team having to manage it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background: var(--soft);">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">Range</span>
    <h2>The Work We Take On</h2>
    <p>Recurring content is the core, but the work spans more than a weekly series. We produced a brand video for Tutoring Rocks at their Nolensville location, filming kids and tutors on site and capturing the local feel of the town. We handled live event coverage for Ballet Ball Nashville with full backstage access, blending the performance on stage with the energy of the night.</p>
    <p>Schools, dance studios, professional services, podcasts: the common thread is a Nashville-area business that needs to look good on camera and needs it on a schedule. Companies like Webb School, Elite Dance, Nolensville Dance Company, and Middle of the Story Podcast trust us to show up and deliver.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <span class="eyebrow">Weddings</span>
    <h2>And a Few Weddings a Year</h2>
    <p>We still pick up a camera for about eight weddings a year, because we love the work and we are good at it. Keeping the number small means every couple gets our full attention and the same cinematic quality our business clients count on. When those bookings are gone for the year, they are gone.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background: var(--soft);">
  <div class="container-narrow text-center">
    <span class="eyebrow">Where we are</span>
    <h2>Rooted in Nashville</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Based in Nashville, TN, serving businesses across Middle Tennessee and beyond. If you have something coming up, or you are tired of video being a once-a-year scramble, let's talk.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
